      <title><![CDATA["Mencius and his Mother: A Lesson Drawn from Weaving" [Literary Excerpt and Illustration]]]></title>
      <link>https://cyh.rrchnm.org/items/show/189</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<div class="element-set">
